  "detailed_description": "BLOCkCORsair is a 2D shooter game where you play as an air pirate in a world where airships come and go, engage in battles, loot, strengthen your own airship, and loot some more.<br>Defeat the most dangerous enemies and become the king of air pirates!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize</h2>Build your own airship by freely assembling dropped parts from enemy ships you have destroyed.<br>Customization is up to you. Create your own original airship and enter a new battlefield.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/4393992b84abaaa3db556f5bca1c4e37.poster.avif?t=1679030318\" width=212 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/4393992b84abaaa3db556f5bca1c4e37.webm?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/4393992b84abaaa3db556f5bca1c4e37.mp4?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >battle</h2>Launch out with a customized airship. When you can't beat the enemy, customize your airship and launch it again.<br>Build a stronger ship and head into battle against challenging enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/a8edc4c5bfb802168fe2169898c13793.poster.avif?t=1679030318\" width=274 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/a8edc4c5bfb802168fe2169898c13793.webm?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/a8edc4c5bfb802168fe2169898c13793.mp4?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "BLOCkCORsair is a 2D shooter game where you play as an air pirate in a world where airships come and go, engage in battles, loot, strengthen your own airship, and loot some more.<br>Defeat the most dangerous enemies and become the king of air pirates!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize</h2>Build your own airship by freely assembling dropped parts from enemy ships you have destroyed.<br>Customization is up to you. Create your own original airship and enter a new battlefield.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/4393992b84abaaa3db556f5bca1c4e37.poster.avif?t=1679030318\" width=212 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/4393992b84abaaa3db556f5bca1c4e37.webm?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/4393992b84abaaa3db556f5bca1c4e37.mp4?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >battle</h2>Launch out with a customized airship. When you can't beat the enemy, customize your airship and launch it again.<br>Build a stronger ship and head into battle against challenging enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/a8edc4c5bfb802168fe2169898c13793.poster.avif?t=1679030318\" width=274 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/a8edc4c5bfb802168fe2169898c13793.webm?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193930/extras/a8edc4c5bfb802168fe2169898c13793.mp4?t=1679030318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
